issue.title: Get Trip API Endpoint
issue.body:
- User will specify start/end location in lat/lon
- User will specify the points of interest in between in lat/lon

- Response will be the optimized route between the start and end going through the points of interest (travelling salesman problem) 
- Response will return the duration time between two points

comment.body: - this PR will add the polylines as multiple points along the leg of the trip so a trip with a start, end, and 2 points of interest in between will generate more points than the 4 points

issue.title: Make API Key Private in Frontend
issue.body:
- Disabling current API key, will need to have frontend use environment variables and use a `.env` file and get the KEY from GOOGLE_API_KEY parameter

- API key in cloud.google.com needs to be enabled with at least these API's
